metadata.title: 2002 (Sep. - Oct.): A Two-leg Survey Leg 2 Data of Waters Between Kodiak and Seward, AK - R/V Miller Freeman (Cruise ID: MF2002-11)
metadata.description: To support research into the physical, chemical, and biological mechanisms acting in the coastal Gulf of Alaska. To make a CTD/Chlorophyll/Nutrient survey of Portlock Bank and northern portion of Albatross Bank and Chiniak Trough.
